&nbsp;

<hr /><!-- Start Bio --><span id="bio">&nbsp;</span>

<div class="well well-lg panel-shadow">
<p class="small"><strong>Command Sgt. Maj. Mark A. Millare</strong> is a combat engineer in the United States Army. He is currently serving as the command sergeant major for the 41st Brigade Engineer Battalion, 2nd Brigade Combat Team, 10th Mountain Division. He previously served as a first sergeant for the 95th Engineer Company (Wolfpack), 84th Engineer Battalion. Millare has deployed three times in support of Operation Iraqi Freedom in Iraq, and once supporting Operation Enduring Freedom in Afghanistan.</p>
</div>
</div>
